column2: SELECT   p.ra,   p.dec, --  s.z, --  s.zErr,   q =    CASE     WHEN p.lnLExp_r < p.lnLDeV_r THEN p.DeVAB_r     WHEN p.lnLExp_r > p.lnLDeV_r THEN p.expAB_r   END,   phi =    CASE     WHEN p.lnLExp_r < p.lnLDeV_r THEN p.DeVPhi_r     WHEN p.lnLExp_r > p.lnLDeV_r THEN p.expPhi_r   END,   p.petroMag_r,   p.petroMag_u,   p.fracDeV_r  FROM photoObj p JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#,#) n ON n.objID = p.objID  WHERE   p.type = #
